  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This property is available to book on bed and breakfast or half-board. For breakfast you can look forward to a tasty buffet from 7.30am – 10:30am. For those on half-board you can enjoy a delicious evening buffet in the Galeria Restaurant.</p>
<p><strong>Galeria Restaurant</strong></p>
<p>For those booked onto half-board, for dinner, you can tuck into a Mediterranean buffet in a contemporary setting with views looking out towards the sea or dine on the large terrace. There is a variety of food on offer and most of the fruit and vegetables served at the hotel are grown on the property - its hard to get fresher than that.</p>
<p><strong>Thai Lounge</strong></p>
<p>Enjoy delicious and nutritious Thai cuisine featuring organic herbs and spices and great atmosphere (bookable and payable locally). </p>
<p><strong>Historic Wine Cellar</strong></p>
<p>The property still has its original wine cellar and offers a weekly Madeiran wine tasting – great for immersing yourself in the history of this property (bookable and payable locally, approx. €6 per person, subject to availability).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
