  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Quinta Splendida Design Spa</strong></p>
<p>The hotels spa is one of the largest on the island with plenty of space to relax and unwind. (Please note that for some room types there is a charge to use the spa, payable locally) You’ll find an indoor swimming pool, relaxation and leisure areas as well as Haman treatment bed, ten treatment rooms and whirlpool. (Massages and treatments are an additional charge and are bookable and payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Botanical Gardens</strong></p>
<p>The hotel has 30,000 m² of beautiful botanical gardens with over 1,000 different varieties of plants and flowers – once a week you can enjoy a guided tour of these extensive gardens (bookable and payable locally, approx. €5 per person, subject to change). You’ll find plants from all over the world here including the Dombeya from Madagascar with its beautiful pink flowers set against its evergreen leaves. Head to the sun terrace next to the Galeria restaurant to find Strelitzia, this majestic flower often nick named the bird of paradise plant is a joy to see.</p>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Large freshwater outdoor swimming pool (open 8am – 8pm)</li>
<li>Cardio fitness room near the outdoor swimming pool</li>
<li>Sun terrace</li>
<li>Table tennis</li>
<li>Pool table</li>
<li>5 hole putting green</li>
<li>Golf services (payable and bookable locally, own transport may be required)</li>
<li>Two bars</li>
<li>Small art gallery</li>
<li>Pool towel service</li>
<li>Parking (bookable and payable locally)</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
