  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>A beautifully-restored 19th Century mansion nestled in the Quinta Splendida Botanical Gardens. The hotel offers a tranquil escape, with restaurants, bars, and a swimming pool on-site, as well as the 30,000 sqm gardens to explore. Within easy walking distance (and accessible via public transport) you can enjoy the small steeply-terraced town of Canico, pebbled beaches, and crystal clear waters.</p>]]></listingDescription>
