  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All rooms are integrated into the botanical garden. Rooms are designed in a typical Mediterranean style and also have use of the outdoor pool, fitness room and table tennis areas. The spa is available at a supplement of approx. €22.50 per person per day for all room types but if you treat yourself to a massage (bookable and payable locally) then you can also enjoy the spa facilities for the day. Those staying in the Spa Sea View Suite have spa access included (massages and treatments are an extra charge, bookable and payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Twin Garden View Rooms</strong> are approx. 20m² and have a balcony or terrace. These rooms sleep two people. </p>
<p><strong>Garden View Studios</strong> are approx. 29m² with views of the beautiful gardens, a kitchenette, balcony or terrace. These rooms sleep two people. </p>
<p><strong>Side Sea View Studios</strong> are approx. 29m² and offer a kitchenette as well as a balcony or terrace. These rooms sleep two people. </p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom Apartments</strong> offer side sea views and are approx. 55m². They offer a well-equipped kitchenette as well as a balcony or terrace. These rooms sleep up to four people. </p>
<p><strong>Spa Sea View Suites</strong> offer a double bed and are approx. 85 – 115 m²  and offer wonderful sea views. Enjoy access to the spa as well as use of the indoor pool. These suites offer a balcony, bathrobes, tea &amp; coffee making facilities and minibar. These rooms sleep two people. </p>
<p>Single Garden Rooms, Single Studio Garden View rooms and Single Studio Side Sea View rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p>Please note that no rooms have air conditioning. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Safe (payable locally, free in spa suites)</li>
<li>TV</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>2pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>12pm</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong><br />A tourist tax of approx. €2.00 per person per night is payable locally for guests age 13 years and over (subject to change).</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
